Author: natecaviar
Title: [ANN][ICO]⚡Solidified introduces SOLID powered Bug Prediction Market! ⚡
Body: No, but we will launch an airdrop campaign. It will be exclusively targeted at Eth. developers and bug hunters. This is necessary to ensure the SOLID token is primarily owned by people who will actually work with it. meaning smart contract authors and auditors + bug hunters.

Author: icohunter1024
Title: [ANN][ICO]⚡Solidified introduces SOLID powered Bug Prediction Market! ⚡
Body: Solid will be the means of a collateralized reputation for the bug hunters. Besides that, it will be the medium of payment for services, which they render. In general, these factors will stake the Solid token when making security assurances. If those assurances turn out to be wrong, they will lose the tokens. Bug hunters and developers will receive priority. For the first month, there will be a 20% discount for Solid tokens.
